class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Infrastructure\\Mercure\\RunTopicPolicy"
type: readonly final class
summary: This class provides utility methods for constructing Mercure topic identifiers based on a run identifier. It encapsulates the logic for generating single and multiple topic strings required for event publication or subscription within the Mercure transport boundary.
